title: "Proof-Carrying Numbers (PCN)"
abstract: "A presentation-layer protocol that enforces numeric fidelity in LLM-generated content through mechanical verification. PCN ensures that numbers displayed to users are verified against source data, highlighting numeric hallucinations when they occur and establishing trust through proof."
